      <item>
        <title>Reaper chill change</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Unknown]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>That change is not effective.<br>
1 chill costs 1 soul, so this might be common.<br>
2 chills cost 3 souls, and 2 chills are the current threshold.<br>
This means that you need to kill 2 people if you want to go crazy without souls for revival and immunity pierce… for something you got for nothing before.<br>
3 chills cost 6 souls, which means 5 kills, aka day 6 if and only if everything goes through and you do not get attacked and when you use it you are in danger of night death.<br>
Do I really need to say you why this is a big reaper nerf and nothing else?</p>
